ham_Aliyevs_official_visit_to_Russia__President_Ilham_Aliyev_met_with_President_Vladimir_Putin_VIDEO-1190763}}</ref>阿利耶夫與俄羅斯和伊朗領導人於2016年在巴庫會面，討論地區內恐怖主義、跨國有組織犯罪、武器走私和販毒。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Leaders of Russia, Iran, Azerbaijan discuss closer ties|work=Daily Herald|agency=Associated Press|url=http://www.dailyherald.com/article/20160808/business/308089876/|access-date=2017-08-23|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224163718/https://www.dailyherald.com/article/20160808/business/308089876/}}</ref>三邊峰會簽署了一項宣言，旨在開發從[[印度|印度]]到[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]的「國際南北運輸走廊」，為現有海上航線提供更好的替代方案。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Baku to host first trilateral meeting of Russian, Azerbaijani, Iranian presidents|language=ru|work=TASS|url=http://tass.com/world/892981|access-date=2017-08-23|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408121148/http://tass.com/world/892981}}</ref>

